{"type":"text","timestamp":1781764488768,"sessionID":"ses_126960be2ffewGSaH1Z0io46OH","part":{"id":"prt_ed9707dd3001TOKnhAa2oF3CvC","messageID":"msg_ed9706d4d001OJ1NNj0YLvJkHC","sessionID":"ses_126960be2ffewGSaH1Z0io46OH","type":"text","text":"The tombstone path does not call `vectorIndex.deleteMemory`; it only updates `memory_index.deleted_at`, so correctness depends entirely on every consumer filtering that column. IвҖҷm checking the high-traffic consumers rather than assuming the flag is safe.","time":{"start":1781764488659,"end":1781764488763},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0028234ca718d9c4016a339188a054819189854212d3b0fca1","phase":"commentary"}}}}
