{"type":"text","timestamp":1781764601358,"sessionID":"ses_126960be2ffewGSaH1Z0io46OH","part":{"id":"prt_ed9723599001lfEZwBN6x8Dj31","messageID":"msg_ed972161b0012HOW9PLyBmyvaL","sessionID":"ses_126960be2ffewGSaH1Z0io46OH","type":"text","text":"The async ingest status handler only reports the queueвҖҷs `job.errors`; because returned `IndexResult` failures are never appended there, callers can see `complete` with no errors for rejected files. IвҖҷm creating the artifact subdirectories now and then writing the report set.","time":{"start":1781764601241,"end":1781764601357},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0c0ab9a6d583de7c016a3391f933448191841b4f203b8e4f58","phase":"commentary"}}}}
